{{Top|leg}}
'''Orowood''' was a high-class area on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] that contained [[Orowood Medcenter]] and [[Orowood Tower]]. It was located twenty [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] east of [[West Championne]] and near the [[Manarai Mountains]].

==History==
Orowood was named after the [[oro wood]] of [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]; it had originally been planned to be a living area for those who survived the [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destruction of Alderaan]]. However, Coruscant was never popular with the Alderaanians, and after the [[Siege of Coruscant]], the remaining Alderaanian refugees also left, and the project was abandoned.

